---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from '../../components/LeadForm.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Nerja Property for Sale | Real Estate in Costa del Sol"
  description="Buy property in Nerja, Costa del Sol. Dramatic cliffs, crystalline coves and a relaxed expat community — at prices well below Marbella."
  canonical="https://realestateincostadelsol.com/costa-del-sol/nerja/"
  ogImage="/og/nerja.jpg"
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-animate style="--anim-delay:100ms">Costa del Sol</span>
      <h1 data-animate style="--anim-delay:220ms">Nerja Property for Sale</h1>
      <p data-animate style="--anim-delay:340ms">Dramatic cliffs, crystal-clear coves, and a laid-back expat community on the eastern Costa del Sol.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="area-content">
    <div class="container area-content__inner">
      <div class="facts-box" data-animate>
        <h3>Nerja Property Market — Quick Facts 2026</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Average price: €2,200/m² (range: €1,400–€4,500/m²)</li>
          <li>Popular zones: Burriana Beach, Capistrano, Maro, Old Town</li>
          <li>Typical budget: €110k–€220k (apartment), €280k–€600k (villa)</li>
          <li>Drive time to Málaga Airport: ~55 minutes</li>
          <li>Drive time to Granada: ~1.5 hours</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 data-animate>Why Buy in Nerja?</h2>
      <p>Nerja is the most easterly major resort on the Costa del Sol, and arguably the most dramatically beautiful. The famous Balcón de Europa promontory overlooks a series of small coves flanked by limestone cliffs — quite different in character to the flat beach resorts further west.</p>
      <p>Nerja attracts buyers who want authentic Spanish character alongside expat conveniences. The town has a large British community, plenty of English-speaking businesses, and a slower pace of life than the busier resorts.</p>

      <h2 data-animate>Key Areas</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Burriana Beach:</strong> Nerja's main beach — apartments here command a premium and let well.</li>
        <li><strong>Capistrano:</strong> Large residential urbanisation on the hills above town. Mix of apartments and villas.</li>
        <li><strong>Maro:</strong> Tiny village 3km east of Nerja. Quieter, more rural, stunning cliffside setting.</li>
        <li><strong>Old Town:</strong> Central apartments, great for rental income, character properties.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="internal-links" data-animate>
        <h3>Related Pages</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/costa-del-sol/">← All Costa del Sol Areas</a></li>
          <li><a href="/homes-for-sale-costa-del-sol/">Homes for Sale on Costa del Sol</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <LeadForm area="Nerja" heading="Looking for Property in Nerja?" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-hero { background: var(--green); padding: 80px 0; }
.page-hero .eyebrow { color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; }
.area-content { padding: 64px 0; background: var(--white); }
.area-content__inner { max-width: 800px; }
.area-content__inner h2 { margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.area-content__inner h2:first-of-type { margin-top: 32px; }
.area-content__inner p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.8; }
.area-content__inner ul { margin: 0 0 16px 20px; }
.area-content__inner li { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.7; }
.facts-box { background: var(--green-lt); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.facts-box h3 { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; }
.facts-box ul { margin-left: 20px; }
.facts-box li { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
.internal-links { background: var(--off-white); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
.internal-links h3 { font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.internal-links ul { margin-left: 0; list-style: none; }
.internal-links li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
.internal-links a { color: var(--green); font-size: 14px; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
